      "Built-in refrigerators protect expensive groceries, prepared food, medication, and in some homes, wine or specialty items that require stable temperature control. Delaying service can turn a manageable repair into food spoilage, water damage, or more extensive mechanical strain. What begins as a fan or sensor issue can become compressor stress if the system keeps trying to compensate.",
