      "Noise level and fit-and-finish also shape the ownership experience. Premium buyers usually notice details such as door feel, interior materials, and how cleanly the refrigerator integrates into surrounding cabinetry. Sub-Zero generally performs well on those points, which helps explain why the brand remains a serious option in upscale renovations and custom homes.",
