      "A premium refrigerator can also be the right fit in condos, brownstones, and renovated homes where appearance matters as much as utility. In those environments, the appliance is part of the architecture. The clean integration, panel-ready options, and established luxury reputation carry real value.",
      "Where the fit is weaker is in short-term ownership plans, highly price-sensitive purchases, or homes where the kitchen does not justify the cost and installation complexity of a built-in luxury unit.",
      "So, Is Sub-Zero the Best Refrigerator?",
